flowchart LR
    U[Student User] --> UI[Smart Campus Event Hub]
    UI --> BROWSE[Browse Events]
    UI --> SEARCH[Search / Filter Events]
    UI --> REGISTER[Event Registration]

    BROWSE --> STORE[(Event Database)]
    SEARCH --> STORE
    REGISTER --> STORE

    STORE --> LIST[Event List]
    LIST --> DETAIL[Event Details]
    STORE --> DASH[Dashboard Summary]

    ADMIN[Organizer / Admin] --> PANEL[Admin Panel]
    PANEL --> STORE
    PANEL --> MANAGE[Create / Update Events]
    MANAGE --> STORE

